This is **Task 4** of my Python Programming Virtual Internship at **Code Sentinel**.  
The task is to create a **Web Scraper** that:
- Fetches HTML content from a website (Hacker News)
- Parses the HTML to extract all headlines
- Displays them as a clean, numbered list

