---

## ğŸ“œ Code Explanation
- **`requests.get()`** â†’ Downloads the webpage HTML  
- **`BeautifulSoup`** â†’ Parses HTML and searches for specific tags/classes  
- **`find_all("span", class_="titleline")`** â†’ Gets all headlines  
- Prints each headline with its link in a numbered list  

